verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Praise the LORD .. Praise the LORD .. Praise the LORD .. Praise , O servants of the LORD.
Praise the LORD .. Praise the LORD .. Praise the name of the LORD.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Who's like the LORD, the LORD our God ... Who's like the LORD, the LORD our God.
Who's like the LORD, the LORD our God ... Who's enthroned on high.
